{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Talon's Blade Features</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/extras/DirectionalCombat.PNG?t=1722542983\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/extras/combat.gif?t=1722542983\" /><br>The directional melee combat system of Talon\u2019s Blade allows you to decide from which direction death reaches your foes. With four possible directions of attack and defense, the combat is both strategic as well as reactionary. Feel the ebb and flow of the fight as you explore the strengths and weaknesses of your foe looking to deal the killing strike.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/extras/ComboMagic.PNG?t=1722542983\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/extras/magic.gif?t=1722542983\" /><br>Successful completion of melee combos will allow you to unleash devastating magical attacks upon your enemies. How this power manifests depends on the combo you choose to perform and the spells you unlock. The more foes you conquer, the more you will be able to upgrade your arsenal of combo-finishing spells.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/extras/Immersive.PNG?t=1722542983\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/extras/landscape.gif?t=1722542983\" /><br>Take control of Marcus Veridious as he embarks on a soul-rending quest for revenge. Make deals with demons, cast powerful spells, brew and utilize potent elixirs, choose who to help and who to abandon, take on ancient ghosts from forgotten worlds, and fight your way to the heart of the corruption that plagues these war-torn lands. <br><br>For 20 years war has been waged across the land. For 20 years the soldiers of the Southern Empire and the Rasnayan Legion have clashed. In a bid to bring the war to a decisive close, the Emperor has sent his elite force of agents, known only as the Talons, on a covert operation with the hopes of turning the tides of war.<br><br>But all is not what it seems within the Empire. Treason has led to the capture and near extinction of the Talons. <br><br>Marauding outlaws and pirates threaten the livelihood of villages on the fringes of the Empire <br><br>Soldiers betray and exploit the very people they swore an oath to protect<br><br>Blood spawn of an ancient and vile demon have ascended from the depths of the earth, driven by the war and chaos that washes the lands above in blood.<br><br>The world, seeded with a plague of war and corruption, has begun to tear itself apart<br><br>Experience the journey of Marcus Veridius as he is set on a path of vengeance to find and kill the ones responsible for the death of his fellow Talons.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1722542983","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/page.bg.jpg?t=1722542983","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1722542983","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1722542983","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Depictions of violence, blood, gore, decapitation, burning alive, being electrocuted, murder, executions, hanging, and death"},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2614960,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Talon's Blade Features</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"h