. In a bid to bring the war to a decisive close, the Emperor has sent his elite force of agents, known only as the Talons, on a covert operation with the hopes of turning the tides of war.<br><br>But all is not what it seems within the Empire. Treason has led to the capture and near extinction of the Talons. <br><br>Marauding outlaws and pirates threaten the livelihood of villages on the fringes of the Empire <br><br>Soldiers betray and exploit the very people they swore an oath to protect<br><br>Blood spawn of an ancient and vile demon have ascended from the depths of the earth, driven by the war and chaos that washes the lands above in blood.<br><br>The world, seeded with a plague of war and corruption, has begun to tear itself apart<br><br>Experience the journey of Marcus Veridius as he is set on a path of vengeance to find and kill the ones responsible for the death of his fellow Talons.","developers":["Soulware"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131460/header.jpg?t=1722542983","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257041024,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041024/movie480.mp4?t=1722026498","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041024/movie_max.mp4?t=1722026498"},"name":"Talon's Blade Early Access Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257041024/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1722026498","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041024/mov